Create an HTML form for issuing certificates, including input fields for recipient name, title, issuer, and metadata.
Add a button to submit the form and call the issueCertificate function on the smart contract using Web3.js.
Create an HTML input field for entering the certificate ID or uploading the certificate file for verification.
Implement a JavaScript function to call the verifyCertificate function on the smart contract using Web3.js and display the verification result.
